 12-minute monologue, or produce multiple bits and taped pieces, or rehears=
e lavish musical numbers, or=E2=80=A6 you get it.<br/> <br/>The idea, I=E2=
=80=99m told, is to make the host gig easier to handle and, thus, more appe=
aling. In an era when hosting the Oscars comes with less upside from the de=
clining audience and more downsides, like the massive time suck and getting=
 eviscerated on social media=E2=80=94for almost no pay, don=E2=80=99t
