assed on the opportunity. To all but a thin sliver of performers (most of w=
hom wouldn=E2=80=99t serve as effective promoters and thus wouldn=E2=80=99t=
 appeal to the Academy or ABC) or the most dutiful of company men (like Kim=
mel, who=E2=80=99s hosted four very funny times=E2=80=A6 or almost every Em=
my host), it=E2=80=99s a polite pass. And I don=E2=80=99t blame them.  <br/=
